            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Hd1e108">Rubrica 4</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De adulatione: blandimento et assentione</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>¶ De adulatione blandimen
      <lb ed="#V" n="18" break="no"/>to et assentione. Rubrica. 4
      
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/><ref>Salomon in prouerb. c.
      <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e127">Si te lactaue
        <lb ed="#V" n="21" break="no"/>rint peccatores: ne quiescas eis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e133"> /
      <ref>c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>27.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e135">Meliora sunt vulnera diligen
        <lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>tis quam fraudientis oscula.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e144">
               <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>
               ¶ <ref>Isocrates in exhortation.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e148">Odi blandientes
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>tanquam decipientes: nam vtrique commissarii fa
        <lb ed="#V" n="26" break="no"/>cti iniuriantur commissis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e156">
               <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>
               ¶ <ref>Aristoteles retho. li. i. c. 20.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e160">Adulationem
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>recipere et adulatorem delectabile est: apparens
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>enim admirator est. Apparens amicus adu
        <lb ed="#V" n="30" break="no"/>lator est. / Li. 2 c. 9. Laudare presentem: adu
        <lb ed="#V" n="31" break="no"/>lationis est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e172"> /
      <ref>Idem ethincorum libro 4. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e174">Omnes
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>blanditores obsequiosi seruiles et humiles
        <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>sunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e182"> /
      <ref>Li. 8. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e184">Amatores adulationis mul
        <lb ed="#V" n="34" break="no"/>ti sunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e190"> /
      <ref>Idem magnorum moralium li. i. c. 51</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e192">Adulator est plus decentibus et existentibus
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>adiiciens.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e200">
               <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>
               ¶ <ref>Terentius. i. comedi scilicet in andria. ca. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e204">Hoc
        <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>tempore obsequium amicos veritas odium parit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e211">
               <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>
               ¶ <ref>Tullius retho. artis noue li. 5. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e215">Habet
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>assentatio iocunda principia: eadem exitus
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>amarissimos affert.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e223">
               <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>
               ¶ <ref>Ouidius sine titulo seu amorum libro i. c. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e227">Im
        <lb ed="#V" n="43" break="no"/>pia sub dulci melle venena latent.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e233">
               <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>
               ¶ <ref>Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum li. 6. e. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e237">Adula
        <lb ed="#V" n="45" break="no"/>tio que similis est amicitie non imitatur tium<!--91.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>illam: sed vincit et preterit: aptis ac propitiis
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>auribus recipitur: ac in precordia ima descen
        <lb ed="#V" n="48" break="no"/>dit: eoipso gratiosa quo ledit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e254"> /
      <ref>Idem in pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="49" break="no"/>uerb.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e256">Habet suum venenum blanda oratio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e262">
               <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>
               ¶ <ref>Auctor li. de formula honeste vite. ca. 4.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e266">Adulatores deuita. Difficillimum continentie
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>opus est assentationes adulantium repellere
        <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>quorum sermones animum quadam voluptate re
        <lb ed="#V" n="54" break="no"/>soluunt. Nullius per assentatione amici
        <lb ed="#V" n="55" break="no"/>tiam merearis: nec hanc promerendi a te adi
        <lb ed="#V" n="56" break="no"/>tum aliis pandas. Non acerba sed blanda
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>verba timebis. Cunctis esto benignus: ne
        <lb ed="#V" n="58" break="no"/>mini blandus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e287">
               <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>
               ¶ <ref>Cato. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e291">Noli homines blandos: nimium
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>sermone probare. Fistula dulce canit vo
        <lb ed="#V" n="61" break="no"/>lucrem: dum decipit auceps.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e300"> /
      <ref>c. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e302">Sermo
        <lb ed="#V" n="62" break="no"/>nes blandos blesosque vitare memento.
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>Simplicitas veri fama est: fraus ficta loquendi</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e310">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>
               ¶ <ref>Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 12. et fi. e. 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e314">Graui
        <lb ed="#V" n="65" break="no"/>us percutit: qui blandiendo crassatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e320"> /
      <ref>Idem
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>de anima. c. 16. et antepenul.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e322">hostis dulcis ami
        <lb ed="#V" n="67" break="no"/>cus amarus est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e330">
               <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>
               ¶ <ref>Uersificator fabularum esopi. 64. fab. et fi.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e334">Blanditie plusquam dira venena nocent.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e340">
               <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>
               ¶ <ref>Montenarius in luna cleri. c. 128. et pe.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e344">Sugit adulator lac pectoris ad vber.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e350">
               <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>
               ¶ <ref>Prouerb. vulgar:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e354">Losenge de enemigo e
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>como passare a panigo.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
